How to use the plugin?

* From v0.5 and on

 The plugin is published on Maven Central and on JBoss Releases repositories. You no longer need to configure your
 Maven settings file.

* Before v0.5

 Before v0.5, the plugin was {{{https://bintray.com/repo/browse/tsegismont/rhq-maven-plugins}published on Bintray}}.

 You must configure your Maven settings file to enable the Bintray repository:

+---
<settings>
 ...
  <profiles>
    ...
    <profile>
      <id>tsegismont-rhq-maven-plugins</id>
      <pluginRepositories>
        <pluginRepository>
          <id>tsegismont-rhq-maven-plugins</id>
          <url>https://dl.bintray.com/content/tsegismont/rhq-maven-plugins</url>
        </pluginRepository>
      </pluginRepositories>
    </profile>
    ...
  </profiles>
  ...
  <activeProfiles>
    ...
    <activeProfile>tsegismont-rhq-maven-plugins</activeProfile>
    ...
  </activeProfiles>
 ...
</settings>
+---
